sendquota plugin for the roundcube webmail

Required Plugins: none

1. copy the "sendquota" folder to your plugin directory.
<install directory>\plugins\sendquota

2. copy config.inc.php.dist as config.inc.php

3. change your database and ldap connection settings in config.inc.php

4. add "sendquota" to your plugin array settings in your <install directory>\config\main.inc.php

$rcmail_config['plugins'][] = 'sendquota';

User quota are now enabled in the roundcube webmail.
You should enable sendquota_log_error and sendquota_log_debug to check your installation.

